00:29:43.904 --> 00:29:45.924
I have somewhat of a more general question.

505
00:29:46.044 --> 00:29:50.024
With more high-grade gliomas or high-risk group two medulloblastoma, where

506
00:29:50.104 --> 00:29:53.844
do you see the room for most improvement in our research and

507
00:29:53.884 --> 00:29:54.624
clinical work,

508
00:29:55.444 --> 00:29:58.924
in the context of this kind of whole genome sequencing and

509
00:29:59.904 --> 00:30:00.824
methylation sequencing?

