00:30:10.536 --> 00:30:14.466
We need to work out how we can give not just multiple drugs in combination, but

514
00:30:14.516 --> 00:30:18.286
actually sequentially give multiple drugs, one after the other.

515
00:30:18.336 --> 00:30:21.316
That's how we cure leukemia. We don't just give one drug.

516
00:30:21.346 --> 00:30:21.536
Well,

517
00:30:22.476 --> 00:30:24.046
maybe blinatumomab now, but

518
00:30:25.116 --> 00:30:27.736
we use lots of drugs in combination. I think that's the key.

519
00:30:29.356 --> 00:30:29.616
Thank you.

520
00:30:29.696 --> 00:30:33.026
Thank you so much, David. That's great. And we'll now welcome our next speaker, Dr.

