00:35:45.636 --> 00:35:49.176
megabase, and there are very few pathways that are recurrently

610
00:35:49.236 --> 00:35:53.016
mutated, perhaps with the exception of a low rate of mutations in the

611
00:35:53.036 --> 00:35:56.784
PI3 kinase MTOR pathway.So while we've

