00:36:04.184 --> 00:36:07.064
And so we really have no biologic subtypes in this disease.

615
00:36:07.504 --> 00:36:11.104
And as I described, we need those to identify therapeutic approaches,

616
00:36:12.024 --> 00:36:12.404
and

