00:55:25.170 --> 00:55:25.760
population.

949
00:55:27.370 --> 00:55:28.610
So thanks for that question, Ryan.

950
00:55:30.210 --> 00:55:30.390
Yes.

951
00:55:31.050 --> 00:55:33.830
So that's not a clinical question, but mechanistic question.

952
00:55:35.890 --> 00:55:39.730
It's incredible that you found that MYC is

953
00:55:39.830 --> 00:55:42.390
a big prognostic factor in osteosarcoma.

954
00:55:43.020 --> 00:55:46.510
In osteosarcoma, you have also lots of chromothripsis, genomic instability, et

